
	SETTINGS UP SASS ENVIROMENTS.
	=============================
	STEP-1 INSTALL NODE.
	https://nodejs.org/en/
	* node -v
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	STEP-2 INSTALL PACKAGE.JSON FILE.
	* npm init
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	PACKAGES WE NEED
	1 - DART-SASS
	2 - BOOTSTRAP
	3 - FONTAWESOME
	4 - AUTOPREFIXER

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	DART-SASS INSTALLTION
	https://www.npmjs.com/package/dart-sass
	* npm install --save-dev sass
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	BOOTSTRAP INSTALLTION
	https://getbootstrap.com/
	* npm install bootstrap --save
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	FONTAWESOME INSTALLTION
	https://fontawesome.com/v5/docs/web/setup/use-package-managers
	* npm install --save @fortawesome/fontawesome-free
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	AUTOPREFIXER INSTALLTION
	https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer#readme
	* npm install postcss-cli autoprefixer
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
	* npm run compile-sass

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

	for the intro section 
	download picture form: https://www.manypixels.co/gallery
	get waves.io from: https://getwaves.io/
	get fonts from : https://fonts.google.com/
	select: regular 400, medium 500, sami-bold 600, bold 700, extra-bold 800, black-900
	get glightbox for video: https://biati-digital.github.io/glightbox/